      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited as a dedicated project car or a comprehensive parts donor. The engine is currently non-operational and will require a significant overhaul or replacement to return to the road. Externally, the body shows substantial wear including noticeable rust patches, faded paint, and several dents. The interior also requires a deep cleaning and upholstery repair, as there are tears in the seating and cracked dashboard components. This is a true fixer-upper for a mechanic or enthusiast who has the time and resources to invest in a total restoration.",
