      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that gets the job done? This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and is ready for its next chapter! While it shows some clear signs of its journey through life\u2014including some cosmetic wear and minor mechanical needs\u2014it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone looking for reliable transportation at a great value. It\u2019s a hardworking car with plenty of character and life left to give!",
