      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to go! It runs super smoothly and is looking for a new owner who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
