    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle body setup and is paired with a precise 6-speed manual transmission. Performance is anchored by a functional M-Variable differential lock and a chassis that has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement. The VANOS system has been serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing across the power band. Suspension components maintain factory-spec kinematics, offering the tactile feedback and lateral stability expected of the chassis. A driver-focused example with all major mechanical vulnerabilities addressed.",
      "price": 31500.0,
