    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small superficial scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is a non-smoker environment, featuring supple leather seats that show only light softening on the driver's side bolster. All electronics, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they should. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no hesitations; I have strictly followed the manufacturer\u2019s service schedule, including a recent oil change and a full brake inspection. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring you won't need a trip to the shop anytime soon. This car is mechanically robust and aesthetically pleasing, ready for its next owner to drive away with complete confidence.",
